  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You may spend a superiority die targeting one allied creature within 30 feet of you. </p><p>When you do, the next time they would make a saving throw of any type, they add half the superiority die to the result. </p><p>On a successful save, you add the same superiority die to your next saving throw before the end of your next turn.</p>",
